original_title: North Mississippi Allstars: Live from Bluebird Theatre Denver, CO - 11.11.11
overview: Music/Musical - On the auspicious day of 11/11/11, the North Mississippi Allstars delivered an amazing performance at the historic Bluebird Theater in Denver, CO. The show represents a watershed moment for the trio, capturing one of the year's best shows.
title: North Mississippi Allstars: Live from Bluebird Theatre Denver, CO - 11.11.11
